name: Chinese zodiac
description:
这是一个十二生肖的lora,你可以通过 pig,bear,chook,monkey,sheep,horse,snake,dragon,bunny,tiger,cow,rat等TAG来控制它。
使用了人物描述以后也可以生成人形。
对场景的改变比较难，你需要加更多的权重
我使用的是sunshinemix_sunlightmixPruned
Lora模型放在这个文件夹下面：\extensions\sd-webui-additional-networks\models\lora

This is a Lora of the Chinese zodiac signs. You can control it with tags such as pig, bear, chook, monkey, sheep, horse, snake, dragon, bunny, tiger, cow, rat, etc.
It is difficult to change the scene, so you need to add more weight.
I'm using sunshinemix_sunlightmixPruned
fter using character description, it is also possible to generate humanoid
The Lora model goes under this folder: \extensions\ sd-webue-additional -networks\models\lora
